CHANGELOG:
- Initial beta release with core functionality
- Full authentication system (email/password)
- PBN file upload with duplicate detection
- Bridge game and hand viewing
- Bidding sequence management
- Comment system for discussions
- User profile and account management
- Admin interface for user management
- Mobile-responsive design
- Production-ready architecture

TECHNICAL STACK:
- Frontend: React 18 + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS
- Backend: Node.js + Express + PostgreSQL
- ORM: Drizzle with type-safe operations
- Authentication: Local email/password system
- UI: Radix UI components with custom styling
- Build: Vite for frontend, ESBuild for backend

READY FOR BETA TESTING:
All core features implemented and tested.
